uotes/#quote\r\n\r\nWhy Use Quotes on Social Media pages?\r\n\r\nQuotes are effectively used to engage with people by many companies. When a famous quote is posted, fans would tend to show their inclination towards the message that the quote tries to convey and respond to it. Quotes are considered as a great engagement tool on Facebook.\r\n\r\nWhy more than 3500 clients have used our services over time? \r\n1. We use only 100% royalty FREE High Quality images\r\n2. We can add your logo and/or website on the quotes for FREE - helps your Branding and drives FREE traffic to your website\r\n3. We design unique quotes for all my clients in less than 48h\r\n4. 100% compatible with the latest Social Media size requirement\r\n \r\nIf you are interested in my services or If you need custom quotes, related to a specific topic or niche, please reply to this email of visit our webpage – http://webtrafficpros.info/quotes'),(21,1,5,'1','kochnaeeum'),(22,1,5,'2','Park'),(23,1,5,'3','(831) 200-5954'),(24,1,5,'4','aroma8355@gmail.com'),(25,1,5,'6','I want to have a 3child teeth checkup.\r\nWhen is it possible?\r\nPlease let me know by e-mail.'),(26,1,6,'1','Shannon'),(27,1,6,'2','Feeney'),(28,1,6,'3','(727) 415-7353'),(29,1,6,'4','sfeeney913@gmail.com'),(30,1,6,'6','I haven\'t been to the dentist in several years. I definitely have a few cavities and I also have 2 chipped teeth I need fixed. I have Delta Dental insurance. I would love an appointment sometime this week if possible. Thank you!!'),(31,1,7,'1','Richard or Joy'),(32,1,7,'2','Bonnett'),(33,1,7,'3','(910) 399-5033'),(34,1,7,'4','jbonnett@ec.rr.com'),(35,1,7,'6','Good morning,\r\nIt\'s not a goodmorning for my hisband.\r\nHe woke this morning with the temp tooth almost gone. He\'s has to remove the tooth. Now, it\'s Sunday he\'s having surgery on Monday. The surgery is at Duke, he can\'t have anything lose in his mouth. He\'s not happy.'),(36,1,8,'1','Justin'),(37,1,8,'2','Stephens'),(38,1,8,'3','(217) 821-1991'),(39,1,8,'4','dmdsupport@dentalmarketdirect.com'),(40,1,8,'6','I know its hard to cut overhead and save money for your office. We have made it easy. Join Dental Market Direct for all your dental supplies and receive the BEST pricing in dental. Average Savings 20%-35%. We have the best pricing on Diamond Burs. You can 1)call your order in 2) send it via computer 3) Scan it on our new app. Convenient. You can join DMD by 1) signing up online 2) calling us. You can start ordering right away or get a quote from us and see what you will save.'),(41,1,9,'1','Meredith'),(42,1,9,'2','Rawlings'),(43,1,9,'3','(859) 494-7981'),(44,1,9,'4','mcrawlings13@gmail.com'),(45,1,9,'6','Need to make an appointment for dental exam'),(46,1,10,'1','John'),(47,1,10,'2','Castillo'),(48,1,10,'3','(914) 200-0021'),(49,1,10,'4','John@Ringboost.com'),(50,1,10,'6','Hi there,\r\n\r\nI wanted to reach out to your company, to let you know 910-DR-SMILE is available to lease or purchase.\r\n\r\nWhile custom phone numbers are a great and powerful marketing tool, their availability is limited. Once the number is sold, it’s gone forever.\r\n \r\nSome of the benefits include…\r\n\r\n*Increase Call Volume & Response Rates\r\n*Stand Out from Your Competition\r\n*Build Brand Awareness\r\n*Make referrals easier\r\n\r\nPlease feel free to contact me anytime for additional details.\r\n\r\nJohn Castillo\r\nDirector of Sales\r\n914-200-0021 (Direct)'),(51,1,11,'1','Jeff'),(52,1,11,'2','Smyth'),(53,1,11,'3','(910) 443-2740'),(54,1,11,'4','jsmyth@ec.rr.com'),(55,1,11,'6','please call me. i need to reschedule my appointment'),(56,1,12,'1','CURTIS'),(57,1,12,'2','MARTIN'),(58,1,12,'3','(910) 616-8940'),(59,1,12,'4','cpa_carolmartin@bellsouth.net'),(60,1,12,'6','Good Morning.\r\nPlease email my latest itemized bill?  I get reimbursed for it. \r\nThank you,\r\nCurtis dob 05/19/62'),(61,1,13,'1','Anna'),(62,1,13,'2','Steinwinter'),(63,1,13,'3','(252) 258-1325'),(64,1,13,'4','asteinwinter@townhallguide.com'),(65,1,13,'6','Town Hall is now preparing Welcome Kits for new families that are moving into our community.\r\n\r\nOur Welcome Kits feature and direct these new families to a small number of local businesses for the goods, services & professionals that they need to find.\r\n\r\nSince our Welcome Kits are exclusive, and we can only accommodate one Dentist, I would ask you to kindly let me know if you are interested in being featured in our local Welcome Kits.\r\n\r\nIt is worthy to note that, according to Dr. Cathy Goodwin in her book “Making the Big Move”, 70% of new residents and families seek out a new Dentist within 6 months of their relocation.  As such, 7 out of 10 recipients of our Welcome Kits are actively looking for a new Dentist.\r\n\r\nI would like to schedule a time when you are expecting me so that I may drop off a sample of our \"Welcome Kit\" and explain the program in greater detail.  \r\n\r\nPlease reply to this email with your availability or call me at your earliest convenience.\r\n\r\nFor a faster response, or if you prefer, feel free to text me on my cell which is listed in my signature.\r\n\r\nThanks.\r\n\r\nAnna Steinwinter\r\n(252) 258-1325\r\nasteinwinter@townhallguide.com'),(66,1,14,'1','Michael'),(67,1,14,'2','Pomponio'),(68,1,14,'3','(301) 440-4759'),(69,1,14,'4','michaelpomponio49@gmail.com'),(70,1,14,'6','I would like to sign up for your Dental Savings Care Program . I have an appointment on 12/12 at 10:30 AM. If there is paperwork that needs to be filled out in advance, please email me the PDF.\r\nThanks!'),(71,1,15,'1','Amanda'),(72,1,15,'2','Beteille'),(73,1,15,'3','(120) 120-1200'),(74,1,15,'4','amandabeteille.online@gmail.com'),(75,1,15,'6','\"Hello,\r\nDo you wish you could increase your online leads? We have helped a lot of businesses thrive in this market and we can help you! Simply hit reply and I’ll share with you the cost and the benefits.\r\nBest Regards\r\n\"'),(76,1,16,'1','Tom'),(77,1,16,'2','Carlin'),(78,1,16,'3','(910) 228-2278'),(79,1,16,'4',