tice. Top Notch!\r\n\r\n[/fusion_testimonial][fusion_testimonial name=\"Tom\" avatar=\"none\" image=\"\" image_border_radius=\"\" company=\"\" link=\"\" target=\"_self\"]\r\n\r\nThe Dentists and Staff are the best in Wilmington. They treat their patients like returning cared about friends, and although they have been in Wilmington for many years they are always up to date on the latest changes and procedures. My family could not be happier.\r\n\r\n[/fusion_testimonial][fusion_testimonial name=\"Linda\" avatar=\"none\" image=\"\" image_border_radius=\"\" company=\"\" link=\"\" target=\"_self\"]\r\n\r\nThe Dental team and staff are professional and friendly and take great effort to insure a painless and comfortable dental experience. I recommend them highly.\r\n\r\n[/fusion_testimonial][fusion_testimonial name=\"Stephanie\" avatar=\"none\" image=\"\" image_border_radius=\"\" company=\"\" link=\"\" target=\"_self\"]\r\n\r\nI have been a patient at Reamer Dentistry for several years and have always received quality service. The dentists and staff are very attentive, caring and just genuinely nice people.\r\n\r\n[/fusion_testimonial][fusion_testimonial name=\"Lorraine\" avatar=\"none\" image=\"\" image_border_radius=\"\" company=\"\" link=\"\" target=\"_self\"]\r\n\r\nWe have been going to Reamer dentistry since we moved to Wilmington in 1980. Very happy with both Drs and all the staff. Thanks all!\r\n\r\n[/fusion_testimonial][fusion_testimonial name=\"Kaye\" avatar=\"none\" image=\"\" image_border_radius=\"\" company=\"\" link=\"\" target=\"_self\"]\r\n\r\nI\'ve been a patient since 1980... wow....35 years! They are like MY family. They care about me and have given the most excellent care.\r\n\r\n[/fusion_testimonial][fusion_testimonial name=\"Val\" avatar=\"male\" image=\"\" image_border_radius=\"\" company=\"\" link=\"\" target=\"_self\"]\r\n\r\nI and my husband has been a patient for approx 30 years and had excellent care and dental work. Would recommend to everyone.